16
00:03:33,070 --> 00:03:35,900
I'll be okay, because...

17
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,870
I'm Sogeking!

18
00:03:40,950 --> 00:03:47,250
In four minutes, the sea train
Rocketman will charge in!

